  OrderIdx: 3
  Title: "H\xC0NH TR\xCCNH H\u1ECCC THU\u1EACT "
  HexCode: 0x190A
  Content:
  - "Ngay t\u1EEB v\u1EA1ch xu\u1EA5t ph\xE1t n\u0103m 2006, UIT \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u1EB7t
    n\u1EC1n m\xF3ng cho k\u1EF7 nguy\xEAn s\u1ED1 b\u1EB1ng ng\xE0nh ________ M\xE1y
    t\xEDnh, n\u01A1i nh\u1EEFng b\u1ED9 \xF3c \u01B0u t\xFA nh\u1EA5t chinh ph\u1EE5c
    \u0111\u1EC9nh cao thu\u1EADt to\xE1n v\xE0 \u0111\xE1nh th\u1EE9c s\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh
    c\u1EE7a tr\xED tu\u1EC7 nh\xE2n t\u1EA1o."
  - "G\u1EAFn b\xF3 v\u1EDBi UIT t\u1EEB thu\u1EDF s\u01A1 khai, ng\xE0nh ____ l\xE0
    n\u01A1i r\xE8n gi\u0169a nh\u1EEFng k\u1EF9 s\u01B0 th\u1EA7m l\u1EB7ng nh\u01B0ng
    quy\u1EC1n l\u1EF1c, nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi x\xE2y \u0111\u1EAFp h\u1EA1
    t\u1EA7ng Internet v\u0129 m\xF4 v\xE0 n\u1EAFm gi\u1EEF sinh m\u1EC7nh c\u1EE7a
    m\u1ECDi k\u1EBFt n\u1ED1i xuy\xEAn l\u1EE5c \u0111\u1ECBa."
  - "Ngo\xE0i ra c\xF2n nh\u1EEFng ng\xE0nh, chuy\xEAn ng\xE0nh h\u1EA5p d\u1EABn
    kh\xE1c. UIT lu\xF4n t\u1EF1 h\xE0o l\xE0 \u0111i\u1EC3m t\u1EF1a th\xE0nh c\xF4ng
    khi t\u1EF7 l\u1EC7 sinh vi\xEAn c\xF3 vi\u1EC7c l\xE0m lu\xF4n n\u1EB1m trong
    nh\xF3m cao nh\u1EA5t n\u01B0\u1EDBc. \u0110\xF3 ch\xEDnh l\xE0 \"qu\u1EA3 ng\u1ECDt\"
    c\u1EE7a h\xE0nh tr\xECnh 20 ________ \u01B0\u01A1m m\u1EA7m t\xE0i n\u0103ng,
    kh\xF4ng ng\u1EEBng ph\xE1 v\u1EE1 gi\u1EDBi h\u1EA1n \u0111\u1EC3 ki\u1EBFn
    t\u1EA1o nh\u1EEFng th\u1EBF h\u1EC7 k\u1EF9 s\u01B0 ch\u1EA5t l\u01B0\u1EE3ng
    cao."
  Keys:
  - key: 6
    value: 'KHOAHOC '
  - key: 4
    value: 'MANGMAYTINH '
  - key: 10
    value: 'NAMHOC '
